WEBVTT

00:01:27.720 --> 00:01:30.536
Turns out, it doesn't really
make good business sense

00:01:30.560 --> 00:01:34.096
to sell someone
a piece of land for eternity.

00:01:34.120 --> 00:01:36.136
(Laughter)

00:01:36.160 --> 00:01:37.776
Whose idea was that?

00:01:37.800 --> 00:01:41.480
In some places, you can't buy a plot
no matter how much money you have.

00:01:42.680 --> 00:01:45.760
As a result, cremation rates
have risen fast.

00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:51.336
In 1950, if you suggested your grandmother
be incinerated after she died,

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:53.760
you'd probably be kicked
from the family deathbed.

00:01:54.520 --> 00:01:58.176
But today, almost half
of Americans choose cremation,

00:01:58.200 --> 00:01:59.520
citing simpler,